{"tid":1358472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[727元朗遊行] 光明正大行入黑社會地頭出得番黎, 就係最好嘅侮辱 - 心態上準備","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:46:13.000Z","uid":31528,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c19d80d041853a80e20d5eafdd2202bc8ce6be03","tid":1358472,"uid":31528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"麻煩睇到呢個POST嘅深呼吸5秒先<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n我星期日晚都有睇元朗直播<br />\n都係嬲到訓唔到<br />\n唔明點解香港作為國際大都會<br />\n可以有呢啲無差別大型恐襲事件發生<br />\n我都好想即刻出黎打柒班牛屎飛<br />\n但係 作為反抗者 <span style=\"color: red;\">一定一定要有大局觀</span><br />\n<br />\n而家香港同中國政府最驚唔係你班仆街出黎遊行示威<br />\n200萬人佢都一樣可以無視<br />\n但係 呢幾日新聞都可以見到港共<span style=\"color: red;\">最驚嘅種子已經種下同萌芽</span><br />\n由以下新聞可以睇到啲端倪<br />\n1.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-shuts-hong-kong-stores-early-as-fears-of-lawlessness-rise-11563793440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fapple-shuts-hong-kong-stores-early-as-fears-of-lawlessness-rise-11563793440&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1Svt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=28a25b89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-shuts-hong-kong-stores-early-as-fears-of-lawlessness-rise-11563793440</a><br />\nWSJ - Apple Shuts Hong Kong Stores Early as Fears of Lawlessness Rise<br />\nConcern grows over the impact of social turmoil on the city&rsquo;s economy<br />\n2.<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5631502/hong-kong-protests-triads-yuen-long/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5631502%2Fhong-kong-protests-triads-yuen-long%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1Svt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=b43f73e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5631502/hong-kong-protests-triads-yuen-long/</a><br />\nTIME - Suspected 'Triad' Gangs Mark Dangerous New Phase in Hong Kong's Crisis<br />\n3.<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5631385/hong-kong-violence-carrie-lam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5631385%2Fhong-kong-violence-carrie-lam%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1Svt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=37eba716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5631385/hong-kong-violence-carrie-lam/</a><br />\nTIME - <a href=\"https://time.com/5631385/hong-kong-violence-carrie-lam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5631385%2Fhong-kong-violence-carrie-lam%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1Svt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=37eba716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5631385/hong-kong-violence-carrie-lam/</a><br />\n<br />\n冇錯, 就係<span style=\"color: red;\">政府同警察無能力去打擊恐襲, 令社會安全蒙上陰影</span><br />\n可以講, 港共呢一步絕對係錯中之錯<br />\n搵黑社會大街大行打人, 仲要俾鏡頭影到警黑合作, 議員背後推動及策劃<br />\n生意人絕對會有安全憂慮, 影響注資決定同投資者心態<br />\n呢一個先係港共政權嘅致命傷<br />\n<br />\n所以, 我覺得我地727元朗, <span style=\"color: red;\">絕對絕對絕對唔可以主動攻擊</span>, <br />\n俾黑材料媒體抹黑我地, 變咗黑衫人恐襲事件<br />\n一定要保持冷靜<br />\n但係如果在場有黑社會開拖<br />\n我地勢必自衛反擊<br />\n記住都係果句, <span style=\"color: red;\">要打 打關節</span>, 唔好打頭 會打死人<br />\n<br />\n今次我地踩入佢地頭<br />\n光明正大遊行落佢地面<br />\n絕對比燒祠堂有用<br />\n班黑社會咁要面, 俾人踩入地頭都冇得反抗, 絕對係對班MK牛屎飛最大嘅侮辱<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">宜</span><br />\n保持冷靜<br />\n一眼關七<br />\n遭攻擊時反擊<br />\n保護身邊人<br />\n出口術笑鳩班黑警同黑社會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勿</span><br />\n憤怒衛昏頭腦<br />\n見人就打<br />\n遊行途中無事無幹 手持明顯係武器嘅野"},{"pid":"133310c47768db9c977f1ebb623a08eba8e23c79","tid":1358472,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cccf643f2f6322b1d17a6bca6afcf0c4ff1e70d3","tid":1358472,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"464a1b8035521685ca539046e01718d3e0f81362","tid":1358472,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6caf3b2fd686378fe625700b1f83f6307dba188","tid":1358472,"uid":31528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"464a1b8035521685ca539046e01718d3e0f81362","tid":1358472,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}